  <abstract>
    <p>
      An open-source and fully reproducible electronic textbook for teaching statistical
      inference using the <c>tidyverse</c> suite of R packages. This book is intended for
      students who are learning R, exploratory data analysis, and the basics of statistical
      inference and modeling. The book assumes no prior experience with coding, statistics,
      or data science.
    </p>
  </abstract>

